node.text: Hey all! We love chatting with you all over the world about buttercream, cake and more! 🌎

node.title: July menu debut and buttercream love💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 19, 2021. May be an image of cake and rose.

node.text: What do you guys think, Too early for fall colors??? We can’t help ourselves thinking about all of the delicious fall menu items we have planned for you next month. Stay tuned for details!!! Both shops open for walk in today, Beachwood 11-6 Solon 12-6 we can’t wait to see your smiling faces!💕 #whiteflowercakeshoppe #instacake #buttercream #buttercreamlove #cake #cleveland

node.text: Some behind the scenes kitchen action!!! Watch as Molly makes a delicious raspberry cake😍 #whiteflowercakeshoppe #buttercream #buttercreamcake #cleveland

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 11, 2021. May be an image of dessert and text.

node.text: Beachwood is hiring! Have you always wanted a behind the scenes look at how White Flower makes it all happen? Wanted a first taste of new flavors before they hit the case? Dreamed of a supportive and tight-knit group of co-workers that become lifelong friends? Then look no further! We’d love to add you to our team! See the second slide for more details and learn how to apply. We will be reaching out quickly to schedule interviews. We can’t wait to meet you!

location.name: The White Flower Cake Shoppe Beachwood

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 11, 2021. May be an image of dessert and text.

Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'OUR BEACHWOOD LOCATION IS LOOKING TO ADD TO THE TEAM! WE ARE HIRING FOR A PART-TIME STORE FRONT EMPLOYEE. THE IDEAL CANDIDATE WILL BE UPBEAT, RELIABLE, AND A TRUE TEAM PLAYER WITH AVAILABILITY ON FRIDAYS AND SATURDAYS. IF THIS SOUNDS LIKE YOU PLEASE EMAIL YOUR RESUME To KHOLTZ@WHITEFLOWERCAKE.COM'.
Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 10, 2021. May be an image of dessert.

node.text: Coffee toffee and Earl grey Macarons are on this months menu😍 Make sure to stop in and try all of our Coffee house inspired treats! #whiteflowercakeshoppe #macarons #cleveland photo by @balsam_bill_hikes

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Our vendor spotlight this week is Shaheena from @onelovecandleco_ I met Shaheena during a cake decorating class a few months ago, this amazing woman has her own local Cleveland company that makes the most incredible dessert inspired soaps, wax melts and candles that we are featuring in our boutiques at both locations! We are proud to support local female owned businesses, please make sure to stop in and purchase some of @onelovecandleco_ items when you stop in for your treats, they make perfect gifts or just to treat yourself! Also my daughter can’t get enough of the succulent soap bar, it smells so good!🌵❤️ #whiteflowercakeshoppe #supportlocal #femaleentrepreneur #cleveland

node.text: What an amazing Ladies night yesterday! Special shout out to Jess and Shivangi for doing such a great job teaching the class, and to all of the fabulous ladies who cake our to have some fun with us! #whiteflowercakeshoppe #buttercream #butercreamflowercake

node.text: Have you heard the news?🎉Simply Sweet cake designs  have been added to our Online Cake Ordering catalog! Head over to the website to check out all of the cakes and sweets you can now order online, choose your cake size, flavor and location for pick up and you will be all set! We do ask for 5 days notice on online orders. Thank you for keeping us so busy we love you all!!! #whiteflowercakeshoppe #buttercream #cleveland
